Greek Finance Minister Venizelos Says Situation ‘Critical’

-- B y   C h r i s t o s   Z i o t i s
-- 
2011-09-22T10:09:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/greek-finance-minister-venizelos-says-situation-critical-.html
Greek Finance Minister Evangelos Venizelos said  Greece  must keep all its commitments in this
“critical” time to avoid following in the steps of  Argentina .  The situation is critical, Venizelos said in a meeting with
President Karolos Papoulias in  Athens  today. Greeks are enduring
a painful attempt to deal with problems and avoid a crisis such
as the one Argentina suffered in 2000, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christos Ziotis in Athens at 
